3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - LDPC codes are widely used in communication systems, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - LDPC codes are also used in network coding and distributed storage systems, which are topics related to social and information networks.
